subject: resource/Moloya_Goswami
object: Moloya Goswami (Assamese: মলয়া গোস্বামী) is a popular actress from Assam, India. She was the first Assamese actress to win the National Film Award for Best Actress for her performance in the Assamese film Firingoti (1992).
